pageContext.claim: “Ballots are being found in riverbeds. They dumped a whole -- they call it a tray. A tray is a lot of ballots I don't know what -- how many, but it's a lot.”
pageContext.analysis: There was no “river” involved. There was some mail found in a ditch in a town in central Wisconsin, apparently discarded, with did not include any known absentee ballots.
